<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1902/481682.jpg" alt="Thank you for voting us the Best Venue of 2018" width="225" height="300">We would like to express our gratitude towards the organising members of AAXO (The Association of African Exhibition Organisers), for choosing us as the Best Venue of 2018. At Gallagher, we pride ourselves on our unmatched service offering and the relationships that we establish with our organisers. We remain committed to continue to offer the service that sets us apart. Our experienced team looks forward to working with you in 2019 and to prove ourselves as the Best Venue in the industry again.